| `POST` | `/api/merchant/auth/login` | Public | Email + password login |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/auth/logout` | Auth | Destroy session |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/auth/change-password` | Auth | Change own password |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/dashboard` | Auth | Revenue, txn count, recent activity |
