| `PATCH` | `/api/merchant/settings` | owner | Update default URLs, contact info |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/keys` | Auth | List API keys (prefix + last used) |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/keys` | owner | Generate new key (returns raw key once) |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/keys/{id}/reveal` | owner | Reveal full key |
| `DELETE` | `/api/merchant/keys/{id}` | owner | Revoke a key |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/webhooks` | Auth | List IPN endpoints |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/webhooks` | owner/dev | Create new endpoint + select events |
| `PATCH` | `/api/merchant/webhooks/{id}` | owner/dev | Update URL, events, toggle active |
| `DELETE` | `/api/merchant/webhooks/{id}` | owner/dev | Delete endpoint |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/webhooks/{id}/test` | owner/dev | Send test ping |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/webhooks/{id}/deliveries` | Auth | View delivery history |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/transactions` | Auth | List own transactions (paginated) |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/transactions/{id}` | Auth | Transaction detail + events |
| `GET` | `/api/merchant/refunds` | Auth | List own refunds |
| `POST` | `/api/merchant/refunds` | owner/dev | Submit refund request |

