## Implementation Order

1. **Database migration** — merchant_users + merchant_sessions tables
2. **DB layer** — `src/db/merchants.rs` CRUD functions
3. **Merchant auth middleware** — `src/api/middleware/merchant_auth.rs`
4. **Merchant auth routes** — login/logout/change-password
5. **Merchant API routes** — dashboard, webhooks, settings, keys, transactions, refunds, deliveries
6. **Main.rs routing** — wire up the new scope
7. **Admin API** — merchant management endpoints
8. **Merchant SPA** — HTML shell + CSS + JavaScript (login, dashboard, all pages including Integration Guide with dynamic code)
9. **Admin panel update** — add Merchants section
10. **Public docs fix** — replace all `your-payvault-domain.com` with `payvault.trialvo.com`
11. **Docs update** — add "Getting Started" for merchant self-service flow

